ther or not Neutrinos do have a none-zero rest-mass. Additionally, we\ndemonstrate that these equations have the potency to explain naturally the\nobserved lepton generation phenomena.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Nov 2007 11:45:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 Dec 2007 19:25:23 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 7 Jan 2008 09:27:39 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 27 Jun 2008 12:15:29 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sat, 6 Sep 2008 08:05:23 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Fri, 22 Jan 2010 00:54:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-01-22"}
